00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:13.771
The infrared lamp Quirumed has an articulated arm

00:00:13.828 --> 00:00:18.514
allowing you to adjust it in several different positions and angles.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:29.600
This way you can direct the radiation to a specific part of the body.

00:00:43.142 --> 00:00:48.340
This article includes a powerful light bulb and a dimmer

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:51.542
to individually adjust radiation heat.

00:00:56.971 --> 00:01:02.340
Its head also allows adjusting the angle and direction of the infrared rays

00:01:02.340 --> 00:01:06.457
in order to achieve greater accuracy in the treatment area.

00:01:08.457 --> 00:01:15.828
Its stable base and its 5 rotating wheels provide a comfortable and easy mobility of the lamp.

00:01:19.028 --> 00:01:23.940
Infrared rays are considerably used in cosmetic

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:28.680
anti-cellulite treatments and anti-obesity being the most popular,

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:32.400
because abesides being relatively cheap, 

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:36.000
it is a treatment that does not damage the tissues.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:45.542
This device also has a strong penetrability, which can heat the deep layer of the skin.

00:01:47.085 --> 00:01:53.370
Its main function is to improve the skin, therefore, this infrared lamp Quirumed

00:01:53.370 --> 00:01:57.942
is ideal for use in a beauty salon or at home.

